All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AcceptablePhrases
    This class outlines all acceptable phrases that a doctor can say for our software to transcribe symptoms and a patient's reasons for visit.
    ConnectToDatabase
    Executable class that will connect the sqlite3 database to the backend.
    Database
    This is my database class, where I read from a database and make the instance of a connection.
    DatabaseSetup
    This class sets up the databases needed for the Apollo platform.
    Datum
    Creates an object for a row in a database table.
    DisplayPatients
    This class is used to display patient information onto the GUI.
    DisplayVisits
    This class is used to display visits into the GUI.
    DoctorRegistration
    This is our registration class that inserts into out doctor table in our database, and 'registers' a new user (doctor).
    Encryption
    This is our encryption class that uses the GOOGLE TINK library.
    Executable
    This is an interface for every executable command.
    FillEHRSections
    This class is needed to produce the summary of visit which corresponds to the symptoms and reasons for visit in the EHR.
    FillSymptoms
    This class is used to find the symptoms reported by a patient during a specific visit.
    FillVisit
    This class fills in the reasons for visit portion of our visit summary.
    KMP
    This class handles the logic for the Knuth-Morris-Pratt (KMP) algorithm for pattern-matching.
    Login
    This is our login class, which authenticates user login via their username and password.
    Main
    The Main class of our project.
    PatientDatum
    Creates an object for patient registered.
    PatientRegistration
    Class to deal with registering a patient into the database.
    RegisterData
    Interface for Registration classes (patient and visit).
    Repl
    This class will build and run the repl.
    ReplHandler
    This class will handle the lines that are read from the repl.
    RunDeepSpeech
    Utility class for running the Speech to text.
    Search
    This interface to be extended by every search algorithm to be used to search a patient visit transcript.
    SearchAllTranscripts
    This class executes the search by keyword on all transcripts from all visits belonging to a doctor for a certain patient.
    ToParse
    This class is used to parse the symptoms found in KMP and give them the correct categorical labeling.
    VisitDatum
    Creates an object for visit registered.
    VisitRegistration
    Class to deal with registering a visit into the database.
